These macros are made available for your personal use and no-cost distribution.
Permission for any other use must be obtained from the author. The most current
version can always be found by following the "Apps" link on my homepage
(http://home.midmaine.com/~rgoertz/Ron/). If you would like to be notified of
updates, send me an email telling me what you like/don't like about
FWCalendar.rexx or FWCAddEvent.rexx.

